Use fill-rule evenodd on fill and stroke dialogue if no flatten result after convert clip to paths.

inkscape:path-effect.helpdata: General Display and position dimension lines and labels Projection Show a line with measurements based on the selected items Options Options for colour, precision, label formatting and display Tips Custom styling: To further customise the styles, use the XML editor to find out the class or ID, then use the Style dialogue to apply a new style. Blacklists: allow to hide some segments or projection steps. Multiple Measure LPEs: In the same object, in conjunction with blacklists,this allows for labels and measurements with different orientations or additional projections. Set Defaults: For every LPE, default values can be set at the bottom.
